    description: 'EGM\'s November 1993 issue revealed the blood activation code for the Sega Genesis version of Mortal Kombat, exposing the stark censorship difference between Nintendo\'s sanitized SNES port and Sega\'s unedited version — and inadvertently fueling the congressional hearings that created the ESRB.',
